{"tid":2004038,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際線聯署]澳洲手足撐反送中比奶共UQ威脅開除","createTime":"2020-05-06T07:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T05:42:00.000Z","uid":239489,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cede033e7d162638476db5ee2f7e05000a8143df","tid":2004038,"uid":239489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:42:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6812/4538865\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6812%2F4538865&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBQ2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=b7164a6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6812/4538865</a><br />\n<strong>澳大學生遭開除威脅 全因他公開批判中國的人權迫害</strong><br />\n//澳大利亞知名的昆士蘭大學，近期再度因一起爭議性十足的秘密聽審會，引起全球關注。該校一名20歲的學生帕夫洛 (Drew Pavlou) 自去年七月在昆士蘭大學舉辦了一場挺香港的和平示威行動後，便開始在校園與社交媒體上，激烈的批評昆士蘭大學與中國共產黨之間的關系，並多次在社交媒體上公開聲援香港的「反送中」示威者，並譴責中國迫害新疆的維吾爾人。<br />\n<br />\n然而，帕夫洛向德國之聲表示，昆士蘭大學上個月突然透過電子郵件，寄給他一份長達186頁的文件，內容包含了校方對他做出的11項指控。根據帕夫洛的說法，大部分的指控都與他過去9個月在校園所發起的抗議行動，或是透過他個人的社交媒體帳號所發表的諷刺言論有關。//<br />\n<br />\n入來簽聯署要求UQ唔好再搞手足！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/the-university-of-queensland-prevent-the-university-of-queensland-from-expelling-drew-pavlou-for-unjust-reasons\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fthe-university-of-queensland-prevent-the-university-of-queensland-from-expelling-drew-pavlou-for-unjust-reasons&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBQ2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=e35299fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/the-university-of-queensland-prevent-the-university-of-queensland-from-expelling-drew-pavlou-for-unjust-reasons</a>"},{"pid":"cbef4c02f676c021639a0d95c454cec25ddb7f46","tid":2004038,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:31:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2ae